          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIU_rm_qUxNtx28xsh3uNbDYxLflceZYNdADQfC-4wy_3s9pg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "This pharmacy has shorted my prescription three months in a row, consistently giving me fewer pills than prescribed. When I finally confronted them about it, they denied any mistake, accused me of lying, and refused to fill my medication going forward. I\u2019m paying $460 a month and only getting 24-27 out of 30 capsules. Charging full price to me, full price to insurance, and yet not giving customers enough to make it through the month.",
