          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-NvxWhWy2fzYUOGvQjLpNhXMqOJ9ozbQtnMkVIUu70Px_NMsPYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I believe this to be the \"Best Pharmacy\" I have ever been to. I actually been going here for about 8 yrs or so. They are great, The head Pharmacist Alec is always helpful and a Kind person. The workers there are also helpful and on point with your medications. All these years that I have been going there I can't think of any problem that my wife or I have had there. There the Best and I'm not from coming from Chelsea so that says a lot. These guys are great and go all out to take care of you as best as they can. They're a great group of guy's and after all these years, I consider them friends because that's how I feel when Im going to get my meds and see them, like Im going to see my friends. My wife and I give them 5 stars for their hospitality, service & friendship. This is one of the best Pharmacist you can find, in my opinion. Shout out to Alec and his crew. You guy's are great. Thanks for all your service, help and friendship. \ud83d\udcaf\ud83d\udc4d\ud83c\udffd\ud83d\ude42\u270c\ud83c\udffd\ud83d\ude09",
