          "description": "The pharmacist, Alex, is a very polite, soft-spoken man. He's very thorough when it comes to ensuring that new prescriptions are compatible with old prescriptions. He always makes himself available to the customers with questions and will give information until you are very clear about your meds. This is a great pharmacy that I trust completely with my life sustaining medicine.",
