          "description": "Great people, I think this is one of the best pharmacies in Chelsea. Very professional and kind. Been going here since it opened, I've been a very happy costumer ever since. I've had no problems getting my medications and if the doctors make a mistake, the pharmacy staff helps to fix it. Such a sweet, little mom and pop shop vibe, it's a gem to this neighborhood.",
